name: AnimeFus - Kyo Mix v0.3
description:
This model is trained with anime characters from KyoAni using Automatic1111.

The model base is Anything v4.0.

-- Please also support --
AnimeChar - Oshi Mix | Hoshino Ai (星野 アイ)
AnimeChar - Tamako Mix | Kitashirakawa Tamako (北白川 たまこ) & Asagiri Shiori (朝霧 史織)

AnimeChar - Liz Bird Mix | Kasaki Nozomi (傘木 希美)

=========================
Revise part of training data, from online web picture, to anime screenshot

  • Revise Training method and parameters

  • Add more training characters

  • This model is not aimed to "copy exact character", but you may try below suggested additional prompt if interested:
    - (Hirasawa Yui:1.1)

    - (Akiyama Mio:1.2)

    - (Nozomi Kasaki:1.2)

  • Lora Files may be provided in futures, stay tune :)

  • Trigger word is optional.
    Internal version code: 0.6.11
